\[\rho_m = \rho_{m, 0} (1+z)^3 
= \Omega_{m, 0} \rho_{\rm cr, 0} (1+z)^3\]

<p>ã“ã“ã§\(\Omega_{m, 0} = \rho_{m, 0} / \rho_{\rm cr, 0}\), \(\rho_{\rm cr, 0} \simeq 2 \times 10^{-29} h^2\), ãã—ã¦\(h = H_0/100{\rm km/s/Mpc}\)ã§ã™ã€‚</p>

\[\rho_r 
= (\Omega_{\gamma, 0} + \Omega_{\nu, 0}) \rho_{\rm cr, 0} (1+z)^4 
\simeq 4.15 \times 10^{-5} h^{2} \rho_{\rm cr, 0} (1+z)^4\]

\[\therefore \Â \frac{\rho_r}{\rho_m} 
= \frac{4.15 \times 10^{-5}}{\Omega_{m, 0} h^2} (1+z) = 1 \ \Longrightarrow \Â 
